'''Bandits''' are found roaming around the [[Bandit Camp]] which is found within level 18 [[Wilderness]]. There are two types of bandits, the only difference between them outside of appearance and examine text is that the bandits with black shirts are aggressive while the bandits with the blue shirts are not. 

